headline: Stitch Fix (SFIX) Reports Q1 Loss, Tops Revenue Estimates
summary: Stitch Fix (SFIX) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 64.29% and 4.17%, respectively, for the quarter ended October 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
